query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `ml_training_data` (
	`id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
	`data_type` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
	`endpoint` varchar(255),
	`method` varchar(10),
	`status_code` int,
	`response_time_ms` int,
	`memory_usage_mb` int,
	`cpu_percent` int,
	`request_data` json,
	`response_data` json,
	`error_data` json,
	`success` int NOT NULL,
	`labels` json,
	`collected_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
	CONSTRAINT `ml_training_data_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `ml_training_sessions` (
	`id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
	`started_at` timestamp NOT NULL,
	`completed_at` timestamp,
	`duration_ms` int,
	`data_points_count` int NOT NULL,
	`data_start_date` timestamp NOT NULL,
	`data_end_date` timestamp NOT NULL,
	`model_type` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
	`model_version` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
	`accuracy_before` int,
	`accuracy_after` int,
	`improvement` int,
	`training_metrics` json,
	`status` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
	`error_message` text,
	`created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
	CONSTRAINT `ml_training_sessions_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
